        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> What about exposing a general mechanism for promoting floating windows to regular ones or pagers?\n\nThis is both already possible (something like `vim.api.nvim_win_set_config(win_id_float, { split = 'right', win = win_id_reference })`) and off-topic (as it asks about a general LSP behavior and not enhancing `vim.pack` functionality).",
